      "title": "Clash at fuel line in Yali",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Jaffna - A person has been admitted to the Jaffna Teaching Hospital with serious injuries in a collision that took place near a fuel filling station in Kulapitti area of \u200b\u200bKokku.",
        "A verbal altercation between people waiting for fuel at the said filling station last night turned into a scuffle, where one person was badly beaten up by a gang."
